precis:
Amendments (SCHEDULE NO. 21) to the TRANSPORTATION OF DANGEROUS GOODS
REGULATIONS which consolidate and clarify the requirements pertaining to
the methods of manufacture, the selection and the use of those means of
containment, and improve the uniform application of those methods for all
modes of transport.
